(function () {
  // Update copyright year
  const copyEl = document.getElementById('copyright-year');
  if (copyEl) {
    copyEl.textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  }
})();






Save the updated main projects page as projects/index.html.
Ensure the detailed project pages (scripting-language.html, task-manager-cli.html, weather-app.html) from the previous updates are in the projects/ directory.
Ensure styles.css and script.js are in the parent directory (as referenced in the HTML with ../styles.css and ../script.js).
The index.html from the previous update (the homepage) should remain in the parent directory.
















